meta_info.name: REVISION_HISTORY_ITEM
meta_info.description: An entry in a revision history, corresponding to a version from a versioned container. Consists of `AUDIT_DETAILS` instances with revision identifier of the revision to which the `AUDIT_DETAILS` instance belongs.

attributes.name: audits
attributes.description: The audits for this revision; there will always be at least one commit audit (which may itself be an `ATTESTATION`), there may also be further attestations.
